          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-4-1632825237625-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, chop the <strong>basil</strong> coarsely (including the stalks)</p><p>Peel and roughly chop the <strong>garlic</strong></p><p>Crumble the <strong>cheddar</strong> into small pieces</p><p>Transfer the <strong>toasted walnuts</strong> to a <strong>food processor</strong> and reserve the pan for later</p><p>Tip: If you don't have a food processor, chop the walnuts with a knife, then add to a pestle & mortar!</p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-5-1632825242491-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-5-1632825242491-x400.jpg",
