            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Cut the <strong>cherry tomatoes</strong> in half</p><p>Fluff the<strong> cooked</strong> <strong>bulgur </strong>then stir through the <strong>halved cherry tomatoes</strong> and <strong>half</strong> of the <strong>walnut & cheddar</strong> <strong>pesto</strong> (reserve the rest for garnish!) – this is your<strong> walnut & cheddar</strong> <strong>pesto bulgur</strong></p><p>Wash the <strong>rocket</strong>, then pat them dry with kitchen paper</p>",
      "order": 7,
